> To make a container and up running:
docker compose up -d

> To verify and check the status:
docker ps

>Connect to database:
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game

>Test database:
SELECT 1;
\q

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
>Start development server:
cd backend
npm run dev

>Test health route:
curl http://localhost:3000/health

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Create Database Tables

>Run SQL file:
docker exec -i pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game < sql/001_init.sql

>Verify tables:
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game
\dt
\q


