To delete a market

>first get a id
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "SELECT id, sport, name FROM events ORDER BY id;"

Then delete by id
docker exec -it pg_prediction_game psql -U pguser -d prediction_game -c "DELETE FROM events WHERE id=16;"                  

  